-- Malaysia's Bank Muamalat to raise up to 2 bln rgt with sukuk
-- 
-- Mon Jun 23, 2014 11:24PM EDT
-- None



KUALA LUMPUR, June 24 (Reuters) - Malaysia's Bank Muamalat [BUKHCM.UL], a unit of sovereign fund Khazanah and auto-to-property conglomerate DRB-Hicom Bhd<DRBM.KL>, will raise up to 2 billion ringgit ($621.7 million) with Islamic bonds, credit agency Malaysian Rating Corp Bhd (MARC) said on Tuesday.

